WEBVTT

00:04:57.836 --> 00:05:00.361
He died rich in fame alone.

00:05:00.361 --> 00:05:03.009
But his treatise on the power of creativity

00:05:03.009 --> 00:05:05.368
and individualism has inspired

00:05:05.368 --> 00:05:06.370
art,

00:05:06.370 --> 00:05:07.502
literature,

00:05:07.502 --> 00:05:09.002
popular culture,

00:05:09.002 --> 00:05:11.419
and even political revolution.

00:05:11.419 --> 00:05:13.292
Don Quixote argues

00:05:13.292 --> 00:05:17.665
that our imagination greatly informs our actions,

00:05:17.665 --> 00:05:19.813
making us capable of change,

00:05:19.815 --> 00:05:22.252
and, indeed, making us human.